	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不太懂什么野餐郊游之类的活动，<delay20 />
那很有趣吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在户外吃便当<delay20 />
可是非常有趣的哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果有需要的话，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也可以帮大家制作便当！<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
