<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请继续写下去吧！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有什么后续啊？<delay8 />
刚才那就写完了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不会吧～<delay frames="40" />
