	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />没什么不好的啊。<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />信上已经给说了
