	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得你说话的语气如果能稍微柔和一点，<delay20 />
给人的印象应该会变好哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什么啊？<delay frames="30" />
现在不是就已经很柔和了吗？<anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还要怎么样才能更柔和一点啊？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是说<tag a="110" b="0" />没法再柔和一点了吗？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />那么就<delay20 />试着改变一下说话方式，
你觉得怎么样？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好吧。<delay frames="40" />
那这样好了，<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的那个“<tag a="110" b="5" />”，<delay8 />
