<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说不定听起来，<delay8 />
会跟平时不太一样对吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Aha" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟平时完全不同，感觉好新鲜！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />看来只要改变一下说话方式，<delay8 />
